# infra/aws/.gitignore — SI-4 / [X2]
#
# Real identifiers (AWS_DEV_ACCOUNT_ID, real ARNs) live ONLY in untracked
# tfvars on the owner's machine. terraform.tfvars.example does not match
# *.tfvars (it ends in .example) and stays tracked with placeholders.
*.tfvars
*.tfvars.json

# Local terraform working state — never committed (state can embed real
# account ids and ARNs [X2]).
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
plan.out
crash.log
crash.*.log

# The dependency lock file IS committed (provider pinning) — keep tracked.
!.terraform.lock.hcl
